'''间谍之妻'''（日语：スパイの妻）是由[[黑澤清|黑澤清]]执导的2020年日本[[時代劇_(日本)|時代]][[爱情片|爱情]][[電視電影|電視電影]]<ref name="variety">{{Cite web|title=Kiyoshi Kurosawa's ''Wife of a Spy'' Picked up by Nikkatsu|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/asia/kiyoshi-kurosawa-wife-of-a-spy-nikkatsu-berlinale-2020-1203510121/|accessdate=2020-07-31|author=Frater|date=2020-02-21|first=Patrick|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝 (雜誌)]]|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302200005/https://variety.com/2020/film/asia/kiyoshi-kurosawa-wife-of-a-spy-nikkatsu-berlinale-2020-1203510121/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="teaser">{{Cite web|title=First Teaser for Kiyoshi Kurosawa's Romance Thriller ''Wife of a Spy''|url=https://thefilmstage.com/first-teaser-for-kiyoshi-kurosawas-romance-thriller-wife-of-a-spy/|accessdate=2020-07-30|author=Raup|date=2020-06-20|first=Jordan|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325173415/https://thefilmstage.com/first-teaser-for-kiyoshi-kurosawas-romance-thriller-wife-of-a-spy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该片由[[蒼井優|蒼井優]]主演，[[高橋一生|高橋一生]]共演。该片的[[剧场版|剧场版]]入选[[第77屆威尼斯影展|第77屆威尼斯影展]]主竞赛单元，并获得[[銀獅獎_(電影)|銀獅獎]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Venice Film Festival 2020 Winners: ''Nomadland'' Takes Golden Lion, Vanessa Kirby Is Best Actress|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/venice-film-festival-2020-winners-list-1234585982/|accessdate=2020-09-12|work=IndieWire|archive-date=2020-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200912180031/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/venice-film-festival-2020-winners-list-1234585982/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。故事背景是[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]時期的[[日本|日本]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=銀熊獎導演濱口龍介加持《間諜之妻》師徒聯手揭黑幕|url=https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10090/5307906|author=聯合新聞網}}</ref>。

